{"tid":509451,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"做緊ACO/CA既大學生，其實你已經比社會淘汰左。","createTime":"2017-12-25T10:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T09:09:16.000Z","uid":125978,"like":21,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6368520c6c5123b32bbf71afcf0b0c1072e14d1c","tid":509451,"uid":125978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T10:22:38.000Z","msg":"私人市場有咁多發展機會，就係冇你份；<br />\n政府中級公務員起薪既工，就係冇你份；<br />\n明明身邊有咁多成功例仔，就偏偏冇你份。<br />\n<br />\n最後唯有去考ACO/CA作為最後容身之所，殊不知地位極低，嚴重超越大學生應有既待遇。<br />\n<br />\n經過各政府部門，眼見如此多坐擁大學學歷既ACO/CA為市民服務，彷如身處於比社會淘汰左既大學生集中營，活生生既人版一覽無遺，場面甚為莊覲，有種說不出既感覺。<br />\n<br />\n做緊ACO/CA既大學生，覺唔覺你已經比社會淘汰左?"},{"pid":"7060e51bc3017548581e082e94ff613807b7c81c","tid":509451,"uid":2349,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T10:24:09.000Z","msg":"高人工過喺出面捱啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：無要ACO offer"},{"pid":"52dc165839363372912b3248b7fc0b4e81cf573b","tid":509451,"uid":53238,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T10:25:03.000Z","msg":"聖誕都發功 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce63761b591ac1f4a326c17301d2bdf6c3c06c84","tid":509451,"uid":37798,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T10:26:04.000Z","msg":"唔覺<br />\n利申 唔係ACO/CO"},{"pid":"d0786acf0a64bb04c263e55f85be72cabe061a1a","tid":509451,"uid":136252,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T10:28:41.000Z","msg":"覺<br />\n<br />\n利申，高過aco max"},{"pid":"7971cff38ccacc2fe53b1098bd4cc96f2a06f5f9","tid":509451,"uid":76747,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T10:32:15.000Z","msg":"連登仔fg未做過野:出面做野好辛苦<br />\n又冇得玩手機 番工冇得hea"},{"pid":"6e90fc70e5737c56ba997ad40645f4d057e73402","tid":509451,"uid":125978,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T10:38:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聖誕都發功 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聖誕節普天同慶，只係一剎那既歡樂，<br />\n你既職業，卻係終身既事。"},{"pid":"