ces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b482662dca652103d80e388274752a4bfec943d7","tid":509451,"uid":48234,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T05:21:18.000Z","msg":"做住ACO準備考professional officer grade又點睇?<br />\n公務員一撚定要唔上進hea足一世,等升CO/SCO就算?屌你老母啦<br />\n出邊做professional officer grade嘅嘢,收ACO起薪點嘅人工仲要冇跳point呢樣嘢<br />\n咁撚差嘅待遇,狗都唔屌啦<br />\n一句講撚晒私人公司D仆街嘢: 通漲咁撚柒勁,人工又唔撚升<br />\n<br />\n入得政府做公務員,多數都係一世都出唔撚返去,最多考更高級公務員<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算出邊私人公司請幾撚多個打手都係冇撚用<br />\n待遇唔好嘅一撚樣大把人離開私人市場考入政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6adb4dd898dd6efd8a7ee74d9862b7b96d66df12","tid":509451,"uid":159333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T05:46:42.000Z","msg":"樓主加油喔<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0fdf5c068acc2e3850987ffcbca5d50e276876","tid":509451,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T05:47:50.000Z","msg":"覺<br />\n<br />\n利伸: pro grade"},{"pid":"bacb4549529a9e3f62cc361aaab0733c5b4be110","tid":509451,"uid":125978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T12:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a7d69966f5ee2730b5622c5365688e6599fdc6","tid":509451,"uid":125978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T23:03:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}